    "In consecutive weeks, students were gradually introduced to the use of AI in writing through the following steps:",
    "Week 1distinguishing AI-generated from human writing 2.",
    "Week 2 -using AI to paraphrase difficult parts of scientific text 3.",
    "Week 3 -using AI to generate answers based on different (unknown and unauthorised) sources 4.",
